# Definition of Done (DoD)

Before coordinator closes a task at Phase 10, verify:

- [ ] All acceptance criteria met; traceability matrix complete
- [ ] Unit tests (and integration if required) green; `run-test-gate.ps1` PASS on full/fast lanes
- [ ] No new warnings/analyzer findings; `dotnet format` clean
- [ ] Code style per `docs/dotnet-code-style.mdc`; AOT check when applicable
- [ ] Docs/OpenAPI updated if contract changed
- [ ] No secrets in diff; secret-scan passed (dev gate)
- [ ] Human review approved (Phase 9)

